async function press(e){const n={normal:"经典版",jobs:"职业版",customized:"自定义版"};await dialog(n[e],`即将开始 Bank Robber ${n[e]}`,"开始")&&(window.location.href=`${e}.html`)}document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded",(()=>{$("#normal").addEventListener("click",(()=>press("normal"))),$("#jobs").addEventListener("click",(()=>press("jobs"))),$("#customized").addEventListener("click",(()=>press("customized")))}));